==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Butcherly
<hw>Butch"er*ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like a butcher; without
compunction; savage; bloody; inhuman; fell.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The victim of a
<xex>butcherly</xex> murder.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>D. Webster.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>What stratagems, how fell, how <qex>butcherly</qex>,⟦br⟧
This deadly quarrel daily doth beget!</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Butcher's broom</ent>⟦br⟧
